'''赫布·萨特'''是著名的[[C++|C++]]程序设计专家。也是{{tsl|en|Dr. Dobb's Journal}}的专栏作家。2002年加入[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]后，成为[[Visual_C++|Visual C++]] [[.NET_Framework|.NET]]的[[技术传播者|技术传播者]]，后升任[[C++/CLI|C++/CLI]]架构的团队领导人。<ref name="sutter_cli">{{cite magazine|url=http://www.ddj.com/cpp/184401790|title=Trip Report: October–December 2003|last=Sutter|first=Herb|date=2004-04-01|magazine=[[Dr._Dobb's_Journal|Dr. Dobb's Journal]]|accessdate=2009-05-21}}</ref>从1999年至2009年1月担任ISO C++标准委员会的秘书与会议召集人，2008年10月这一职位被{{tsl|en|P. J. Plauger}}接手，后在2009年10月{{tsl|en|P. J. Plauger}}辞职后重新接任。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://herbsutter.com/2010/03/03/where-can-you-get-the-iso-c-standard-and-what-does-open-standard-mean/ |author=Herb Sutter |work=Sutter's Mill |title=Where can you get the ISO C++ standard, and what does "open standard" mean? |date=2010-03-03 |accessdate=2011-10-16 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118065156/https://herbsutter.com/2010/03/03/where-can-you-get-the-iso-c-standard-and-what-does-open-standard-mean/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite report |url=http://www.open-std.org/jtc1/sc22/wg21/docs/papers/2009/n3003.pdf |author=Stefanus Du Toit |title=Minutes of WG21 Meeting, October 19, 2009 |website=Open Standards |date=2009-12-04 |accessdate=2010-04-10 |pages=10, 20–21 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506015935/http://www.open-std.org/jtc1/sc22/wg21/docs/papers/2009/n3003.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite mailing list |url=https://groups.google.com/group/comp.std.c++/browse_thread/thread/a8e772c69e71b73e/56cc158874ada8e7?show_docid=56cc158874ada8e7&fwc=1# |title=Plauger resigned as convener? |date=2009-10-25 |accessdate=22 May 2020 |mailing-list=comp.std.c++ |author=George Ryan |author2=Ville Voutilainen |author3=Francis Glassborow |author4=Steve Clamage |archive-date=2013-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616035131/http://groups.google.com/group/comp.std.c++/browse_thread/thread/a8e772c69e71b73e/56cc158874ada8e7?show_docid=56cc158874ada8e7&fwc=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 近年来Sutter是[[C++/CX|C++/CX]]和[[C++_AMP|C++ AMP]]的主要设计者。<ref name="sutter_bio">{{cite web |url=http://herbsutter.com/about/ |title=About |accessdate=2012-10-30 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227042835/https://herbsutter.com/about/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

