== 免费的午餐已经结束 ==
"The Free Lunch Is Over"是一篇著名文章<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Sutter |first=H. |date=2005 |title=The free lunch is over: A fundamental turn toward concurrency in software |magazine=Dr. Dobb's Journal |volume=30 |issue=3 |url=http://www.gotw.ca/publications/concurrency-ddj.htm |access-date=2020-08-29 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301074217/http://gotw.ca/publications/concurrency-ddj.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>发表于2005年。阐述了[[微处理器|微处理器]]的主频已经达到了物理极限，导致了两个后果：
* 处理器制造商将聚焦于[[多线程|多线程]]产品技术， 
* 软件开发者将开发大规模[[多线程|多线程]]程序。

